    <item>
      <title>图斯克称波兰将加快乌克兰加入欧盟的谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/poland-to-speed-up-ukraine-s-eu-accession-talks-tusk-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克周三表示，波兰将在现任欧盟轮值主席国六个月期间寻求加快乌克兰加入欧盟的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/poland-to-speed-up-ukraine-s-eu-accession-talks-tusk-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 13:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称里夫斯将在未来多年担任英国财政大臣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-says-reeves-to-be-uk-chancellor-for-many-years-to-come</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，雷切尔·里夫斯将在“未来许多年”担任英国财政大臣，这是英国首相在市场动荡打击英国资产、使其地位备受关注之后，给予其财政大臣迄今为止最有力的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-says-reeves-to-be-uk-chancellor-for-many-years-to-come</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 12:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国众议院通过法案，放开酒类生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/thailand-s-lower-house-passes-bill-to-free-up-liquor-production</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国众议院通过了一项法案，鼓励小企业主发展酒类生产。泰国总理巴东丹·西那瓦称，此举将有助于打破泰国酒类饮料行业的垄断，支持农村经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/thailand-s-lower-house-passes-bill-to-free-up-liquor-production</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 11:58:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
