    <item>
      <title>保加利亚组建内阁以结束政治僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bulgaria-moves-forward-with-cabinet-to-break-political-deadlock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚中右翼政党试图打破僵局，提议组建联合政府，为这个巴尔干国家提供通过有效多数解决腐败和采用欧元等问题的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bulgaria-moves-forward-with-cabinet-to-break-political-deadlock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:24:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利、阿联酋、阿尔巴尼亚签署 10 亿欧元海底能源电缆协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/italy-uae-albania-sign-1-billion-deal-for-subsea-energy-cable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼在阿布扎比表示，意大利、阿尔巴尼亚和阿联酋将共同制定一项计划，通过亚得里亚海海底电缆将电力从阿尔巴尼亚输送到意大利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/italy-uae-albania-sign-1-billion-deal-for-subsea-energy-cable</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:10:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电在中美脱钩进程中对美、日投资创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/taiwan-investments-in-us-japan-surge-as-china-figure-stagnates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，台湾企业对美国和日本的投资创下了历史新高，而对中国大陆的投资则停滞不前——凸显了两岸关系恶化导致的供应链转移。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/taiwan-investments-in-us-japan-surge-as-china-figure-stagnates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
